dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Eau Claire County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2016. There are feature classes within the geodatabase, EauClaire_Hydro_2016.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'EAUCLAIRE_HYDROLINE_2016' and 'EAU_CLAIRE_HYDROPOLY_2016'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
